56.3	Stephen_Merchant	Stephen Merchant	Stephen James Merchant (born 24 November 1974) is an English writer, director, radio presenter, comedian, and actor. He is best known for his collaborations with Ricky Gervais, as the co-writer and co-director of the popular British sitcom The Office, as the co-writer, co-director and a co-star of Extras, and as the co-host of The Ricky Gervais Show in its radio, podcast, audiobook and television-show forms. The Ricky Gervais Show in radio form has won a bronze Sony Award.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/StephenMerchantAltNov09.jpg/220px-StephenMerchantAltNov09.jpg
